item.title: Sample blog post to learn markdown tips
item.description: {: .box-success} This is a demo post to show you how to write blog posts with markdown. I strongly encourage you to take 5 minutes to learn how to write in markdown - it’ll teach you how to transform regular text into bold/italics/tables/etc.I also encourage you to look at the code that created this post to learn some more advanced tips about using markdown in Beautiful Jekyll.
